                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "不稳定孢子云"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成4点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素伤害</span>，消耗所有<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">活化激能</span>层数，每层使此伤害+1。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/03/47826599/515b825928f7e1ba52ff024f82afd1f8_7111784788391568808.png",
                "id": "talent95066",
                "key": "尾羽豪放",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "尾羽豪放"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被动技能</span></p><p>【被动】战斗开始时，初始附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">活化激能</span>。</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/03/47826599/8eda35aa45e48dcada8e955719c1bfd1_2810343469383876894.png",
                "id": "talent86354",
                "key": "活化激能",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "活化激能"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着草元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">绽放</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下次火元素或雷元素伤害+2的[<span style=\"color: white\">草原核</span>]</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">燃烧</span>：本伤害+1，生成回合结束时造成1点火元素伤害的[<span style=\"color: white\">燃烧烈焰</span>]（可用次数1，最多叠加到2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">原激化</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下2次草元素或雷元素伤害+1的[<span style=\"color: white\">激化领域</span>]</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/05/47826599/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_2397857129027225162.png",
                "id": "talent31435",
                "key": "草元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "草元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">活化激能</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">本角色造成或受到元素伤害后：</span>累积1层<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">「活化激能」</span>。（最多累积3层）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>如果<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">「活化激能」</span>层数已达到上限，就将其清空。同时，角色失去所有充能。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/05/47826599/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_5206518276073401140.png",
